name: Eames_Style_White_Molded_Plastic_Side_Chair
description: The Eames Style Side Chair will look fabulous in any home, restaurant or commercial office. The slender yet sturdy solid wood dowel legs and Eiffel-style frame complement and support a seat made of tough plastic. However you use this Side Chair it is sure to mold itself to your needs. These chairs are robust enough to take the pressure in a commercial setting and they provide stylish comfort with clean lines. Immediately recognizable for its Eiffel tower frame crafted from beech, the original DSW Chair was one of the first plastic chairs to be mass produced. Its popularity is well deserved, with a strong yet flexible polypropylene seat, perfectly contoured for maximum comfort. The profile is striking, combining bright colors with strong, wood legs to create a look that is classic yet contemporary in any setting.
